tourBios.curYearHigh: Finished T10 at the PGA Professional Natinal Championship. Shot a competitive course record 66 in the final round at the Philadelphia Cricket Club's Wissahickon Course...Played in the PGA TOUR's Human Challenge, missing the cut.
tourBios.carHigh:
2014: Won second consecutive Southern California Northern Chapter Player of the Year honor, the fifth time he's received that honor...Won the Southern California PGA Championship,l posting a competitive course-record 67 in the final round at the Alisal Ranch Course.

2013: For a fourth time, was the Southern California Northern Chapter Player of the Year.

2012 Won the Northern Chapter Championship for a second time, six years after his first title. 

2010: Named the Southern California Northern Chapter Player of the Year for a third time...Was ninth at the Southern California PGA Championship.

2007: Earned Southern California Northern Chapter Player of the Year for a second consecutive season...Finished fifth at the Southern California PGA Championship.

2006: Named the Southern California Northern Chapter Player of the Year...Won the Southern California PGA Assistants' Championship...Also captured the Northern Chapter Championship.
tourBios.personal: Director of instruction at Oakmont CC in Glendale, Calif.
